<H1>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </H1>
<H1>CCM</H1>
<ul>
  <li><font size="5">Forms part of CORBA 3.0 as specified by OMG</font></li>
  <li><font size="5">Defines a component model including component contracts, 
  component life cycle definitions, state management, and multiple interface 
  support</font></li>
  <li><font size="5">A home interface is defined that provides factory 
  operations to create, destroy, or find the desired component</font></li>
  <li><font size="5">Each component can have multiple interfaces or facets</font></li>
  <li><font size="5">The CORBA persistence service is used to provide 
  container-managed persistence</font></li>
  <li><font size="5">A distributed event model is defined</font></li>
  <li><font size="6">CCM gaining importance!</font></li>
</ul>
